Ingredients.1: 4 (4 inch) street taco corn tortillas (such as Mission®)

Directions.1: Preheat an air fryer to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C).

Directions.2: Place a mini muffin tin pan upside down the air fryer basket. Position tortillas in the indents of the muffin tin. Place the basket on the lowest rack of the air fryer oven.

Directions.3: Air fry until golden brown and crispy, about 3 minutes. Remove tortillas from mini muffin tin pan and place upside down in the basket. Air fry until bottom side is crispy and golden brown, 1 minute more.
